|GKB-- Earthquake -----------------------------------------------|000

Exerting control through the Tellurian current, the druid
causes a massive upheaval of the earth, similar to
an earthquake.  While this invocation will not harm the
druids or their followers, others will take a
certain amount of damage, regardless of armor, and
will be unable to move or fight effectively for
some time.

